column11: geneID = id taken from the gff file. Used because there are features that lack both geneNames and bNums
bNum =  b number from the gff file
Differential expression columns reports the if the FDR adjusted p-value is less than 0.0167
Direction of regulation reports if the gene is positively or negatively regulated by RpoS, or not significantly regulated
Sensitivity reports if the gene is linear, sensitive, insensitive, or not significantly regulated by RpoS.
